						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/S-T-Issues/Reducing-Postharvest-Losses-A-Challenge-for-the-Scientific-Community/Related-developments/Managing-thrips-caused-crop-losses-educating-future-scientists" title="Managing thrips-caused crop losses, educating future scientists" alt="link">Managing thrips-caused crop losses, educating future scientists</a></h2>

	
					<p>Thrips-transmitted tospoviruses affect fruits and vegetables. The research team will study how these viruses spread and contribute to the evolution of new strains and try to understanding how management techniques applied in one region might work in another.<a href="http://www.plantmanagementnetwork.org/pub/php/news/2013/ManagingThrips/" target="_self">http://www.plantmanagementnetwork.org/pub/php/news/2013/ManagingThrips/</a>(Plant Management Network, 28/03/2013)</p>
