					<p>â€˜Postharvest technological initiatives to improve food security and market access' &nbsp;Dates: 1â€“5 July 2013 &nbsp;Venue: Hyatt Hotel, Port of Spain, Trinidad &nbsp;The Postharvest Working group of The International Society for Horticultural Science (ISHS) has embarked on a biannual conference entitled â€˜Postharvest and Quality Management of Horticultural Products of Interest for Tropical Regionsâ€™.</p>
