					<p><b>







 




  
  

	
	<a href="/var/knowledge/storage/images/media/images/img_1593/503394-1-eng-GB/IMG_1593.jpg" rel="lightbox[]" >	
	  </a>
	
	
	
	
  	






	 
  





	</b>The CTA Postharvest policy writeshop took place in August 2013 as planned. The purpose was to discuss the results and lessons learned from the CTA commissioned case studies undertaken in Trinidad &amp; Tobago, Ghana and Senegal, and other initiatives for influencing future policy and practice on postharvest. The presentations and key messages are available. The synthesis report and policy brief are under preparation and will be made available subsequently.Download the summary report here.</p>
